Conway's Game of Life
=====================

*author*:  Y H
*date*:    27/06/2016

Generate a grid of random values (1 or 0) and play Conway's Game of Life 
according to the rules specified at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway%27s_Game_of_Life

**Interface:** 
	  <kbd>Left Mouse Button</kbd>:  Pause/Start
	  <kbd>Right Mouse Button</kbd>: Start New Instance
	  <kbd>Left Arrow Key</kbd>: Last State (1 state back only)
	  <kbd>Right Arrow Key</kbd>: Next State (Get Next Generation)

**Color Codes**: 
    **Orange:**    Alive
    **Yellow:**     Born
    **DarkBlue:** Died
    **Black:**       Dead

